examples.en: Wisps of steam rose up from the teapot.
There was a wisp of sun coming through the mist.
A wisp of hair had escaped from under her hat.
examples.ru: Из-под её шляпы выбилась прядь волос.

examples.en: The sun had gone down, a little wisp of a new moon was following it.
examples.ru: Солнце село, и затем показался тонкий серп нарождающейся луны.

examples.en: Wisps of smoke rose into the air.
Wisps of cotton candy clung to his mouth.
examples.ru: К его губам прилипли кусочки сладкой ваты.
